","content":"尝试更新到最新版本，检查是否能正常使用。"},"193":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"cp ~/.hydro/addon.json ~/.hydro/addon.json.bak 备份插件列表。"},"194":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"hydrooj addon list 查看插件列表，并使用 hydrooj addon remove 名称 禁用所有非官方提供的插件（即不含 @hydrooj/ 前缀的插件）"},"195":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"重启检查是否正常运行。"},"196":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"如果能够运行，则为第三方插件导致，可按顺序尝试加载刚刚禁用的插件，检查是否出现异常，联系对应插件提供方解决。"},"197":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#hydrooj","content":"如果不能正常运行，请向开发组提供自 Hydro 开始启动至触发故障的完整日志以便于诊断问题。"},"198":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"指前端页面无法加载（持续转圈或是左下角黄色 / 红色错误提示）"},"199":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"使用 Ctrl+Shift+Delete 清除浏览器缓存再试。"},"200":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"更新 chrome 浏览器至最新版尝试。"},"201":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"同上，尝试禁用第三方插件。"},"202":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"如果问题仍未解决，打开 F12 开发者控制台，转到 Console (控制台) 标签页，查看是否有报错信息。"},"203":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/FAQ/debug#前端异常","content":"打开 Network (网络) 标签页，查看是否有请求失败的情况。"},"204":{"id":"/docs/Hyd