提交数量限制，若无特殊需求我们建议您停用 Codeforces VJudge。"},"841":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","content":"此文档已过时，仅作留存使用，以下教程仅为示例，如想了解详细安装方法请前往 FAQS(常用教程) 查看具体使用指南。"},"842":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","content":"部分支持的远程站点对提交数量/访问次数/访问来源有一定限制，Hydro 不保证 VJudge 的 100% 可用性。"},"843":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge#codeforces","content":"安装插件后创建名为 codeforces 的域，进入数据库 db.domain.updateOne({_id:'codeforces'},{$set:{mount:'codeforces'}});"},"844":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge#codeforces","content":"在 codeforces 的域设置中，将 allowedLangs 如下配置（在新版即在允许提交的语言中选中所有 codeforces 开头的语言）："},"845":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge#codeforces","content":"在 vjudge 表中插入如下条目："},"846":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge#codeforces","content":"将如下配置添加至 langs 设置末尾："},"847":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/plugins/vjudge#codeforces","content":"之后再重启 Hydro 即可。"},"848":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"page","content":"使用内容分发网络","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn"},"849":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"资源 CDN"},"850":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全站 CDN"},"851":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","content":"如您希望改善 Hydro 的访问质量，在您的服务器带宽较小的情况下，您可以考虑使用内容分发网络，即 CDN ，通常情况下您仅需设置资源 CDN 即可大幅度改善访问质量，关于如何使用内容分发网络和使用中的任何问题请联系各大云厂商。"},"852":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"创建并配置好资源 CDN ，在控制面板中将 server.cdn 设置项修改为 CDN 域名。（如 https://cdn.hydro.ac/，以 / 结尾）。"},"853":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#资源-cdn","content":"CDN 的回源地址配置为源站，缓存时间可按需设置（推荐一个星期或更久）并放行 CORS 和 Referer（可能名为防盗链），设置允许空 Referer 请求。"},"854":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"如果您预算充足，可以使用全站 CDN。"},"855":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全站 CDN 配置较为繁琐，如您没有相关使用经验请仅建立并配置资源 CDN ，配置资源 CDN 在大部分情况下即可大幅度改善访问质量。\n因各服务商全站 CDN 配置方法不同，配置过程不同，需要配置的内容较多，以下仅为参考配置，如果有任何问题建议先查阅云服务商文档及咨询云服务商工程师。"},"856":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"配置全站 CDN 时需要启用 CDN 的 WebSocket 支持（不同服务商开启方式可能不同，且可能额外收费），否则会导致评测状态无法自动更新/IDE无法使用等等问题。请确认仅缓存了资源文件！否则可能导致用户登录状态混乱。"},"857":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"缓存设置可以参考以下设置："},"858":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"类型"},"859":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"内容"},"860":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"缓存行为"},"861":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cdn#全站-cdn","content":"全部文件"},"