tem/cli-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#创建评测账号","content":"您需要留意运行此指令返回的数字，表示该用户的 uid，需要填入下面的指令中，然后给予该账号评测权限。"},"888":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#创建评测账号","content":"完成后将配置的用户名及密码写入评测机配置文件，评测机即可连接到网页端。"},"889":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#黑名单相关","content":"用户封禁："},"890":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#黑名单相关","content":"IP/邮箱域名封禁："},"891":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#命令列表","content":"所有于 此文件夹 下的函数均可用 cli 调用。"},"892":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/cli#命令列表","content":"这里并没有列出所有可以运行的指令，因为其中很多功能我们更推荐通过 Web 访问。"},"893":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"page","content":"数据库备份和恢复","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database"},"894":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"进入数据库"},"895":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"快速备份与恢复"},"896":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#增量备份","content":"增量备份"},"897":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动备份","content":"手动备份"},"898":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动恢复备份","content":"手动恢复备份"},"899":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"非常不推荐直接操作数据库！"},"900":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"当你改动一个字段的时候，可能与其相关的部分忘记修改，改完觉得好像没什么问题，过段时间发现了一些异常，根本不会想到是你这次改数据库导致的，之后又不会修。"},"901":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"直接修改数据库后，可能没有通知主程序，缓存仍然存在，表现为修改不生效。"},"902":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"直接操作数据库的权限过大，若操作失误带来的影响通常是灾难性的。"},"903":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"在绝大部分情况下均不需要/不可以直接操作数据库。若确需要，可使用 hydrooj db 命令打开数据库 shell，也可以从 ~/.hydro/config.json 查找数据库 connection string 并使用外部工具进行连接。"},"904":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#进入数据库","content":"注：MongoDB 的用户是附加在特定数据库中的，使用外部工具连接请确保使用了正确的 authSource 选项。"},"905":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"为了保证数据安全，请定期备份。"},"906":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"若您使用自动脚本安装，可使用 hydrooj backup 快捷备份数据，备份完成后会在当前目录生成备份压缩包文件，您可使用 hydrooj restore <备份文件路径> 恢复之前备份的数据。"},"907":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"备份支持以下参数："},"908":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"--dbOnly 跳过文件备份，仅备份数据库。"},"909":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"--withAddons 同时备份安装的插件"},"910":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#快速备份与恢复","content":"--withLogs 同时备份系统日志"},"911":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#增量备份","content":"自 Hydro 5.0.0-beta.6 版本起，支持基于 restic 进行增量备份。首次使用请先执行 restic init 初始化一个存储库，之后使用 hydrooj backup -r 存储库地址 -p 存储库密码 进行备份。"},"912":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动备份","content":"可使用 MongoDB 自带的 mongodump 进行数据库备份。并将 /data/file 文件夹备份即可。"},"913":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动备份","content":"对于数据库，请请不要在数据库运行时直接拷贝数据库文件夹。请每次备份后检查生成的备份文件的大小和内容，确保备份成功。请不要把备份数据和 Hydro 系统放在同一台机器上，这样数据丢失的风险仍然较高。"},"914":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/database","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/database#手动恢复备份","content":"使用 MongoDB 自带的 mongorestore 导入备份的数据库文件，并还原 /data/file 目录文件。如果只是想不同机器之间迁移部署，只需要在停止 Hydro 和 MongoDB 服务后将相关文件夹（通常为 /data/db 与 /data/file 与 /root/.hydro/config.json ）复制即可。"},"915":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"page","content":"前端修改","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify"},"916":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面翻译或是添加新语言","content":"修改页面翻译或是添加新语言："},"917":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"修改页面模板："},"918":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"此指南将教您修改前端文件。"},"919":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"如果您正在使用开发者模式，请直接修改 packages/ui-default/templates 下的文件。"},"920":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"如果您使用安装脚本部署："},"921":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","content":"请先使用 hydrooj addon create 创建一个本地插件（如果之前没有做过的话）。"},"922":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面翻译或是添加新语言","content":"修改翻译：在 zh.yaml 内搜索您需要修改的翻译内容，并将 其所在行而非整个文件 修改后添加至 ~/addon/locales/zh.yaml 。"},"923":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面翻译或是添加新语言","content":"添加语言：可参照 zh.yaml 格式创建一个新文件。欢迎社区参与多国化翻译工作。"},"924":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"通常的，在您访问的 url 前加上 view-source:（如 view-source:https://hydro.ac 即可查看页面源代码，在第二行的 <html data-page=\"xxx\"> 中 data-page 值即为页面名（首页例外，为 main.html）。\n在 默认 templates 中找到对应文件，将文件的全部内容 复制到 ~/addon/templates/ 文件夹下后进行修改即可。"},"925":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"特别的，创建题目时的默认模板位于 partials/problem_default.md，创建训练计划时的默认模板位于 partials/training_default.json，修改方式同上。"},"926":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/frontend-modify#修改页面模板","content":"以上所有更改均会在重启 Hydro 后生效。"},"927":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"page","content":"导入用户","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user"},"928":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"目前支持 csv 格式（用 , 分隔）或 Excel 格式（用 TAB 分隔） 导入用户数据, 数据既可以用文本编辑器创建，也可以用 Excel 等软件来辅助创建。"},"929":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"每行最少三列，最多五列，分别为: 邮箱，用户名，密码，显示名，用户信息。（显示名和用户信息为可选）请使用 UTF-8 编码，否则中文可能会乱码。如果使用 CSV 格式（逗号分隔），则用户信息列不可用。"},"930":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"可以在粘贴后点击预览验证复制入的数据的有效性"},"931":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"这将创建三个用户："},"932":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"user1 密码为 password1 , 邮箱 foo@undefined.moe；"},"933":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"user2 密码为 password2 ，邮箱 bar@undefined.moe，显示名为 temp；"},"934":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"user3 密码为 password3，邮箱 test@undefined.moe，显示名为 test，学校为 Hydro School，学号为 123，该用户将会被分配至当前域的 class1 小组内；"},"935":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/import-user","content":"用户创建后无法删除，请谨慎操作"},"936":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintai