aintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"mongodb： MongoDB 数据库"},"949":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"caddy： 反向代理"},"950":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#进程名称","content":"后文的指令中将用 <name> 替代此处的进程名称，用 <id> 替代进程 ID（进程 ID 可通过 pm2 ls 查看）。（尖括号同样需要替换）"},"951":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"在部分环境（常见于 lxc 容器或是精简版系统）下，服务器重启后 Hydro 可能不能正常自启动，这时请使用 pm2 resurrect 手动载入进程列表。"},"952":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"如果手动修改进程列表且已经覆盖掉保存的原列表，请使用 pm2 stop all && pm2 del all 清空所有进程之后重新运行安装脚本。原有数据不会丢失。"},"953":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#pm2-基本指令","content":"Hydro 主进程同样支持多进程启动，但在中低端服务器（不超过4核）中没有必要使用多进程启动 Hydro，会降低性能且成倍提高内存占用。"},"954":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#更新","content":"Hydro 系统会不定期发布更新，可以使用下面的命令获取更新。"},"955":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/maintain#更新","content":"无特殊情况请 不要更新PM2 ！此操作可能导致进程列表丢失！"},"956":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","type":"page","content":"现场赛指南","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest"},"957":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/system/onsite-contest","content":"参照 XCPC-Tools"},"958":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/copy-problem","type":"pa