"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"公告： 域主页上显示的公告，创建后可以更改。"},"983":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"avatar： 域头像，与用户头像同理，可以使用 gravatar:email 或 qq:id 或 github:name 或 url:link 的格式添加。将会在“我的域”界面内显示。"},"984":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建域","content":"创建域后，您将在此域中拥有管理员权限，可以在域内进行添加题目/创建比赛等操作。"},"985":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#初始化讨论节点","content":"您可以在“管理域”选项卡中点击“初始化讨论节点”按钮初始化讨论节点。"},"986":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"Hydro v5 开始，未登录的用户和未加入域的用户在域内默认 guest 权限，加入域的用户默认使用 default 权限。您可以在加域管理中设置 允许用户自助加入域，分配 default 权限。以获得和 v4 相同的权限效果。在 v5 中，只有加域用户会显示在域排行榜中。域管理员修改特定用户的权限为除 default 或 guest 之外的权限后，该用户加入域时将可以绕过其他条件要求，并在加入域时自动应用分配的角色。将用户的权限显式设置为 guest 可以防止用户使用自助加域功能加入域。加域后可以主动退出或被管理员踢出域，此时用户权限组还原为 guest，直至再次加入域。只有已经加入的域会在 “我的域” 中显示。用户注册后会自动加入 system 域，并不可主动退出。"},"987":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"在 Hydro v4 至 Hydro v5 的升级过程中，将执行以下操作："},"988":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"标记所有现有用户为已加入"},"989":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v5","content":"将未设置加域条件与设置为没有用户可以自助加入的域设置为允许所有用户自助加入，权限分配为 default"},"990":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v4","content":"未登录用户将默认使用 guest 权限，登录用户将默认使用 default 权限。（所以将登陆用户设为 default 权限后并不会显示在“管理用户”页内，这也表示所有用户默认不会出现在管理列表中）所以将一个用户的权限设为 default 和将用户移出该域是等价的。"},"991":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-21","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#hydro-v4","content":"对于不在列表中的用户，点击右上角“添加用户”，在左侧选中用户，右侧选择权限组，再点击“确定”即可。"},"992":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-22","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建比赛作业","content":"若您想要创建比赛/作业，您可以在“比赛”或“作业”选项卡中，在页面右侧找到“创建”按钮，\n题目一栏支持根据题目ID或是题目名自动筛选。设置完后可点击“创建”按钮创建比赛（描述这类的框不知道写啥就随便填，不能留空）。"},"993":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-23","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建比赛作业","content":"若因为删除作业/比赛内题目导致无法打开，可以通过 /contest/<id>/edit 或 /homework/<id>/edit（即在无法打开的页面页面后加上 /edit）直接访问编辑页并修正。"},"994":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-24","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"若您想要创建训练，您可以在“训练” 项卡中点击“新建训练计划”，填写以下信息："},"995":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-25","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"标题：该训练的标题；"},"996":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-26","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"简介：该训练的简介，会与标题同时显示在列表页面中；"},"997":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-27","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"说明：该训练的详细信息；"},"998":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-28","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"计划：该训练的具体题目及计划信息，其格式如下："},"999":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-29","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"其中，“章节详细信息”的包含以下部分："},"1000":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-30","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"_id：章节数字编号；"},"1001":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-31","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"title：章节标题；"},"1002":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-32","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"requireNids：训练此章节之前需要完成的章节数字编号，若无要求则留空，若有多个则使用逗号分隔；"},"1003":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-33","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"pids：此章节中包含的题目的 ID，若有多个则使用逗号分隔。"},"1004":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-34","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"举例：若要在训练中创建三个章节，章节中分别有 ID 为 1，2，3 的题目。其中章节一、二无前置条件，章节三需要同时完成章节一、二后才能进行，则格式如下："},"1005":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain-35","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/domain#创建训练","content":"若因为删除训练计划内题目导致训练计划无法打开，可以通过 /training/<id>/edit（即训练计划页面后加上 /edit）直接访问训练计划编辑页并修正配置文件。"},"1006":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"page","content":"用户文档","url":"/docs/Hydro/user"},"1007":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"题目难度"},"1008":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#参与比赛","content":"参与比赛"},"1009":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"发布讨论"},"1010":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#认领作业","content":"认领作业"},"1011":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"Hydro 中题目的难度，根据递交数、通过率以及每个递交的递交时间和评测结果，通过算法计算得出。"},"1012":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"一般地，难度的数值越大，该题目越难。"},"1013":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"新题目的难度可能不准确；在题目获得大量递交之后，难度才会变得较为准确。"},"1014":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"越早递交评测的用户代码的评测结果对题目难度影响越大。"},"1015":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#题目难度","content":"题目的难度由算法计算得出，有可能出现不准确的结果。"},"1016":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#参与比赛","content":"您可以在比赛的详细界面内点击“参与比赛”按钮进行参与。\n比赛过程中“成绩表”会根据比赛规则显示排名。\n在比赛截止之后，您仍然可以订正其中的题目，但“成绩表”将停止更新。"},"1017":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"若您想发布一个讨论，请先进入一个讨论节点，之后点击“创建一个讨论”按钮并填写："},"1018":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"标题；"},"1019":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"内容；"},"1020":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"是否高亮：若选择后，该贴的左边将有醒目的红色线条（需要“高亮讨论”权限）；"},"1021":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"Pin：该讨论是否置顶（需要“置顶讨论”权限）。"},"1022":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#发布讨论","content":"之后点击“创建”按钮进行发布。"},"1023":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user#认领作业","content":"您可以在作业的详情页面中，点击“认领作业”。在作业开始之前，您无法查看作业中的题目。在作业持续时间内，您与他人的做题情况会被实时统计在“成绩表”内。在作业进入延期阶段后，您仍然可以提交题目，但成绩表内的分数将根据延期扣分规则按百分比折算。在作业截止之后，您仍然可以订正其中的题目，但“成绩表”将停止更新。"},"1024":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"page","content":"权限系统","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission"},"1025":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"Privilege"},"1026":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#permission","content":"Permission"},"1027":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"角色"},"1028":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#加入域","content":"加入域"},"1029":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v5","content":"Hydro v5"},"1030":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v4","content":"Hydro v4"},"1031":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","content":"Hydro 的权限系统使用双层结构，分别为 Privilege (PRIV) 和 Permission (PERM)。权限在系统内部使用位运算表示，具体的定义与数值可以查看 源代码 。"},"1032":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"Privilege 是用户在整套系统内拥有的权限，在所有域均生效。如创建用户，编辑系统设置，创建域，查看域等等。"},"1033":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"特别地，PRIV.PRIV_USER_PROFILE 控制一个账号是否能够作为普通账号登录。若不具有此权限，该账号将无法登录（被封禁）。"},"1034":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"常见需求："},"1035":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"若不想让普通用户上传文件 可以关闭default角色的 PRIV_CREATE_FILE 权限"},"1036":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#privilege","content":"若需要关闭站内消息 可以关闭对应的 PRIV_SEND_MESSAGE 权限"},"1037":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#permission","content":"Permission 是用户在单个域内拥有的权限，如创建题目/比赛，发布/删除讨论等等。"},"1038":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#permission","content":"如果 PERM.PERM_VIEW 被禁用，则该用户无法查看此域。"},"1039":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"通常我们需要给特定的一组用户分配相同的权限。在用户量较多的时候这会非常混乱难以管理，为此我们设计了【角色】，便于批量操作与管理。角色是针对域内权限（PERM）的。在系统内置了三个角色："},"1040":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"guest （对未登录用户生效，含已封禁用户）"},"1041":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"default （对所有未指定角色的用户生效，包括未加入域的用户）"},"1042":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"root （拥有所有权限）"},"1043":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-18","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#角色","content":"通常情况下，如果需要对域做特殊的权限控制，应当新建一个用户组（例如 member）并将选定用户加入该用户组。将角色移出域和将用户的角色设置为 default 是等价的。若有需要，您也可以创建 teacher, admin 等其他角色。考虑到系统中的用户可能非常多（数万甚至数十万），在用户列表中仅会显示权限不为 default 的用户。"},"1044":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-19","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v5","content":"见 域 章节中的说明。"},"1045":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission-20","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/permission#hydro-v4","content":"加入域的过程实际上是 用户通过某种方式自助将自己的权限组由 default 变更到另一权限组（如member） 的过程。因此在入域申请链接的权限组中选择 guest 和 default 是没有意义的。"},"1046":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"page","content":"Hydro常见题型的制做心得","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create"},"1047":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-0","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"零. hydro题目存储格式"},"1048":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-1","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#一-制做最简单的oj题目","content":"一 制做最简单的OJ题目"},"1049":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-2","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#二函数交互型题目","content":"二、函数交互型题目"},"1050":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-3","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#三半对拍-自己指定评测程序并修改测试输出格式","content":"三,半对拍-自己指定评测程序并修改测试输出格式"},"1051":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-4","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#四-全自动对拍题","content":"四. 全自动对拍题"},"1052":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-5","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#五文件读写测试","content":"五.文件读写测试"},"1053":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-6","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#六子任务测试","content":"六,子任务测试."},"1054":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-7","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#七客观题制做","content":"七,客观题制做"},"1055":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-8","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"heading","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#八小结","content":"八.小结"},"1056":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-9","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","content":"作者: laomaiqq: 29985091网址: http://82.157.98.222:8888/日期: 2022/03/16"},"1057":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-10","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","content":"本文为作者使用hydro时的实验记录，希望对大家有帮助.包括如下内容"},"1058":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-11","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","content":"零. hydro题目存储格式一. 制做最简单的oj题二. 含有自定义头文件的oj题，即函数交互式的题目三. 半自动对拍的oj题，即不需要录入预期输出的题四. 完全对拍题，即不需要录入输入数据和输出数据的题五. 指定输入文件和输出文件六. 多个子任务七. 客观题，即制做有标准答案的填空和选择题."},"1059":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-12","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"如果想在本地建立好题目，然后批量上传的话. 下面的格式应该对你有帮助每个题目应自占一个目录，目录名为题目编号比如1 ，2，3，4等等.每个题目目录下一般有下面的元素：problem_zh.md 这个文件是就是题目的内容，即题目的描述，是一个markdown格式的文档.probelm.yaml 文件.这个是题目的配置信息. 比如标题和标签等。testdata 子目录，对应网站里的测试数据部分里的文件，里面至少有一个config.yaml文件 用来说明测试的类型.具体内容见后面的例子如果题目有测试用例，则每个用例至少要提供一个in文件和一个输出文件(但有些测试类型不用，详情见后)additional_file子目录用来存放给做题者用的额外文件，比如头文件，图片，pdf文档等，在题目的 markdown 文档中可以用下面的格式为这些文件提供下载链接：提示文字"},"1060":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-13","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"下面为手工录入各种题型的步骤，即在网站登录后点创建题目之后的操作.如下图所示"},"1061":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-14","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#零-hydro题目存储格式","content":"我们假定题目内容均为下面的markdown文档"},"1062":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-15","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#一-制做最简单的oj题目","content":"题目网址: http://82.157.98.222:8888/p/P10000"},"1063":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-16","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#一-制做最简单的oj题目","content":"新建题目之后编辑题目内容，输入题号和标题，然后点创建按钮。如下图所示."},"1064":{"id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create-17","page_id":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create","type":"text","url":"/docs/Hydro/user/problem-create#一-制做最简